    "name": "Neverway",
    "steam_appid": 2318330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Neverway》融合了恐怖、生活模拟和动作角色扮演元素。菲奥娜辞职后，在一座农场重新开始生活，并成为了一位已逝之神的不朽使者。努力别让自己的生活分崩离析，同时寻找 Neverway ——这个噩梦世界正在逐渐渗入你的现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/3607e070c86a4f9c34b0006b1a218359.apng?t=1755200872\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/3607e070c86a4f9c34b0006b1a218359.poster.avif?t=1755200872\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=168 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>由《蔚蓝(Celeste)》的像素艺术家联合执导，并由Disasterpeace负责音乐制作。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/91b61c956cd176eea33ef7fbb4caef77.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与超过10位魅力超凡的角色相会（或约会！）；他们拥有独立的日常和故事线。每段关系的建立都能解锁增益效果和战斗能力，让你的旅程更加轻松。你会选择对他们撒谎，还是坦诚相待？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/378ae653f2b827b8d4bc306b962fe74a.avif?t=1755200872\" width=594 height=546 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/9edfde607a095cd3ae2a4979eb272bbc.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Neverway》采用俯视角的快节奏战斗系统，注重玩家的个性化表达。通过制作物品来定制你的游戏风格，并通过与角色建立友谊来解锁战斗能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/60ee11efad7d37d7b92a6f8351eddd8e.poster.avif?t=1755200872\" width=594 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/60ee11efad7d37d7b92a6f8351eddd8e.webm?t=1755200872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/0b6c31f3e0f956d6603aeaa6f633d2f4.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植农作物、制作物品、准备餐点，或是心无旁骛地装饰你的家园。时间分为三个时段：早晨、下午和晚上，你可以选择何时推进到下一个时段。夜以继日，逐步前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/b242d7413f20a20fa6176cf5d693b687.poster.avif?t=1755200872\" width=594 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/b242d7413f20a20fa6176cf5d693b687.webm?t=1755200872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/b9d38a0badfc35cc58cca9b3a5aed7f2.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 由《蔚蓝(Celeste)》的像素艺术家联合创作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由Disasterpeace制作原声音轨</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款渐进式恐怖RPG，带有动态过场动画</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与超过10位魅力超凡的角色相会（或约会！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快节奏战斗，专为键盘与控制器优化</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作物品和战斗能力，定制你的游戏风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在偏僻的岛屿上耕种、钓鱼、制作，建立全新的生活</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/508c2609dc6f299f3500e629f9c909d8.poster.avif?t=1755200872\" width=594 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/508c2609dc6f299f3500e629f9c909d8.webm?t=1755200872\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/1033a9e5d47f56e703d4ad11c7bec576.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>记住，要不惜一切代价，偿还你的债务……</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/c985f5bcfdfe70319493c66f6a0a8599.apng?t=1755200872\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/c985f5bcfdfe70319493c66f6a0a8599.poster.avif?t=1755200872\" class=\"bb_img\" width=596 height=128 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2318330/extras/3510e12e3e8095b8ddee9a71883e033c.avif?t=1755200872\" width=596 height=68 /></span></p>",
